&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job purpose&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;aCommerce is the region’s leading ecommerce service provider. With over 800 talented staff and operations in Indonesia, Thailand, Malaysia, Singapore and the Philippines.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a highly skilled, cross-functional &lt;strong&gt;Lead AI Consultant&lt;/strong&gt;. In this role, you will embed with various business units—including Supply Chain, Marketing, Inventory Control, Accounting, and Finance, back office operations —to diagnose operational challenges, gather complex requirements, and architect high-impact, AI-driven solutions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You are the ultimate translator. You possess both the acute business acumen of a Business Analyst to uncover real-world problems and the deep programming proficiency needed to convert those problems into granular, technical blueprints. Your primary deliverable is a production-ready technical design that our dedicated AI development team can seamlessly execute.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Core Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Internal Business Consulting:&lt;/strong&gt; Partner directly with leadership and domain experts across Marketing, Supply Chain, Inventory, and Finance to deeply understand their workflows, identify pain points, and uncover data-driven optimization opportunities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Business &amp;amp; Systems Analysis:&lt;/strong&gt; Extract, analyze, and document complex business rules, transforming vague departmental needs into highly structured functional and technical product requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AI Solution Blueprinting:&lt;/strong&gt; Design end-to-end technical blueprints and system architectures for AI products. This includes defining data pipelines, data model structures, API integrations, and model performance metrics (e.g., accuracy thresholds) so that engineering teams can build with minimal ambiguity.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Technical Feasibility &amp;amp; Prototyping:&lt;/strong&gt; Leverage your programming background to validate data availability, query databases, and build occasional quick proofs-of-concept (PoCs) to prove feasibility before handing work over to the core development team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Product Lifecycle Management:&lt;/strong&gt; Own the product lifecycle from initial discovery through delivery. Define the minimum viable product (MVP) scope, manage risk, and ensure the engineering output aligns perfectly with the original business intent.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Required Technical &amp;amp; Professional Skills&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1. Hands-On Technical Programming (Proficient Level)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Because you will be designing the technical framework for the AI development team, you must speak their language fluently. Hands-on coding testing will be part of our interview process.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Python:&lt;/strong&gt; Proficient in data analysis, manipulating data structures, and working with core AI/ML packages.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SQL:&lt;/strong&gt; Expert-level capability to write complex queries, joins, and aggregations across relational databases to locate and assess business data.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;C++:&lt;/strong&gt; Strong understanding of object-oriented programming, memory management, and compiled logic to architect high-performance components or system integrations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;JavaScript / TypeScript:&lt;/strong&gt; Capable of understanding web architecture, front-end data handling, or building simple prototype UIs to demonstrate how an AI feature will look to the end-user.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2. Business Analysis &amp;amp; Domain Knowledge&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated experience translati

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job purpose&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Lead, Communication Planning is the creative engine behind our Live Streaming success. Your mission is to design tactical communication plans and innovative content mechanics that turn viewers into buyers. You will drive Sustainable Growth by balancing high-energy creativity with a sharp focus on Profitability and GMV improvement across all live platforms.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Live Tactical Strategy&lt;/strong&gt;: Lead the end-to-end communication planning for Live Streaming (TikTok, Shopee, Lazada), focusing on high-conversion scripts, flows, and tactical hooks.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Creative Growth Mechanics:&lt;/strong&gt; Develop and pilot new, out-of-the-box creative tactics and interactive mechanics to drive immediate GMV improvement and engagement.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Brand Strategy Customization:&lt;/strong&gt; Tailor communication plans for each brand partner to ensure their unique value proposition drives sustainable sales growth.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Planning &amp;amp; Organizing:&lt;/strong&gt; Oversee the live streaming calendar and coordinate with KOLs, production, and brand teams to ensure all plans are delivered on time with zero missed deadlines.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Performance Analysis:&lt;/strong&gt; Use analytical thinking to evaluate live stream data, identifying key drivers for revenue and areas for profitability optimization.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Result-Oriented Execution:&lt;/strong&gt; Take full accountability for campaign outcomes, ensuring all tactical communication leads to measurable business growth and &quot;WOW&quot; service standards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Requirements:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Minimum 5 years of experience in Communication Planning, Content Strategy, or Live Stream Management.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Platform Specialist: At least 2 years of hands-on experience specifically with TikTok or Ecommerce platforms (Shopee, Lazada), with a focus on Live Streaming and tactical campaign management.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Tactical Creativity: Proven track record of creating content or live mechanics that drive immediate commercial results (Drive Revenue).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ecommerce Insight: Deep knowledge of the TikTok/Marketplace ecosystems, algorithm trends, and audience behaviors.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analytical Thinking: Strong ability to turn live stream data/metrics into actionable strategy pivots to ensure profitability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strategic Communication: Excellent presentation and storytelling skills in both Thai and English.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Agility &amp;amp; Accountability: A self-starter who thrives in a fast-paced environment and takes 100% ownership of project success (Result Oriented).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;u&gt;Content Strategy &amp;amp; Planning&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and execute weekly and monthly content calendars for livestream programming.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify content opportunities, trends, and audience insights to inform planning decisions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create end-to-end content concepts and show frameworks for various livestream formats (entertainment, commerce, educational, creator-led, etc.).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;u&gt;Programming &amp;amp; Execution&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee the planning and rollout of key live campaigns, peak seasons, and thematic events.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate with Creators, KOLs, Partners, and internal teams to deliver high-quality and on-brand livestream content.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure all content elements (scripts, run-downs, creative assets, talking points) are prepared ahead of each show.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;u&gt;Performance Optimization&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor livestream performance metrics (CTR, retention, watch time, GMV, conversion).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Run content reviews and post-mortems to identify improvement points.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Propose content optimization strategies such as improvements in storytelling, pacing, anchors, creator selection, and formats.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;u&gt;Cross-functional Collaboration&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with Creator Management, Live Stream, and Ops Teams to align on content direction and resources.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with the Commercial team to align content with category priorities and sales targets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure seamless operational execution across teams for all live shows.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Requirement &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s degree in Marketing, Communications, Marketing Communication or a related field&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Min 2 years experience of live commerce or live marketing ideally in E-Commerce&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The ability to work and thrive in a fast-paced, rapidly changing work environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong interest in digital marketing tools and tactics, include knowledge of social media.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be Creative, keep up with the latest trend&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong writing, communication and analytical skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Able to work independently and teamwork, result-oriented&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Willing to be placed in Bekasi, Jawa Barat&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job purpose&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Lead - Marketing Planning &amp;amp; Strategy is a challenging role that provides an opportunity for you to build your own team and grow our client’s businesses. You will get to see the total picture of the business, marketing media optimizing (AdWords, Facebook, CRM, SEO etc), and deliver beyond impressions and clicks and getting deep into anything that helps drive sales including promotion strategy or website optimization.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be the owner of client’s success, responsible for overall client performance and satisfaction&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Plan client roadmaps based on their objectives, backed by data or industry best practices&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Set up a work process in order to get tasks completed with good quality and in time. Manage client expectations by clearly indicating deadlines and scope of work&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor budget, performance, and key metrics closely throughout the month&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with media optimization team to execute plans to meet budget, targets and deadlines&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide performance reports by data and analyses, demonstrating deep understanding of each media channel and areas that clients need help in (ecommerce, lead generation or branding)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Initiate ways to improve client performance and team efficiency&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Consult and grow client’s businesses by developing data-driven sound online marketing strategies and media plans that meet business objectives, as well as suggest best practices to clients to have best-in-class ecommerce website&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify new opportunities to upsell aCommerce services with current clients&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mentor and coach 1-3 junior team members&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Requirements&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in client-facing or consulting roles such as Account/Project Manager or Sales&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;In-depth knowledge and understanding in Google Analytics as well as online marketing media channels&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analytical, able to work with data and analyze it to find insights and come up with next steps&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong organization and problem solving skills with the ability to lead, manage and execute multiple projects quickly and efficiently&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Good communication and presentation skill, able to keep every stakeholder aligned and updated&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proactive, with the ability to work well independently and as a team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Professional, positive attitude with a strong work ethic and willingness to learn&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in ecommerce or managing own shops is a big plus (no need to be an ecommerce site – Instagram, Facebook or any other shops are fine)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monthly and quarterly business review&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay up to date with best practices, new tools, and technologies&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understand the team’s challenges by managing the end-to-end process: research, campaign planning, production, performance monitoring, campaign optimization, reporting and consultation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Responsible for driving initiatives to achieve our client’s business objective (often revenue or number of lead) using social media advertising, search advertising (Google, Yahoo, and Bing), display advertising, YouTube advertising, and mobile application advertising&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyze and optimize the campaign portfolio using the data-driven technique. Then, develop strategies to grow the business&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Channel performance evaluations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Requirements&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2-4 years of experience and knowledge in Digital Marketing is a must!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong Google Marketing Platform knowledge is preferred.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong analytical skills and experience generating performance reports&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Have a team management experience.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Eagerness to learn and adopt new tools/technologies as well as share knowledge with others&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A self-starting attitude – the ability to work independently and take initiatives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to manage multiple projects simultaneously&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work as a team and with clients&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Good command of MS Office, MS-EXCEL, MS-POWERPOINT, MS-WORD&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Technical Expertise:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage live stream software(OBS,Tiktok live studio) and platforms (TikTok Live, Shopee Live, Lazada Live, etc.) to ensure optimal performance and troubleshoot technical glitches.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor live streams for any technical issues or disruptions, and take swift action to resolve them.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain a strong understanding of streaming protocols and best practices across various platforms.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Content Moderation:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Actively monitor chat messages and comments for inappropriate content, hate speech, or violations of community guidelines.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage comments promptly to maintain a positive and inclusive environment for viewers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work collaboratively with the live anchor to address viewer concerns or questions that require moderator intervention.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Stream Support:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist the live anchor with pre-stream preparations, including setting up equipment and testing software.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor scripts and product information to ensure accuracy and provide real-time support during the stream.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Generate reports on live stream performance metrics (viewership, engagement) for post-analysis.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Teamwork and Communication:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate effectively with the live anchor, marketing team, and technical staff to ensure a seamless live stream experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Clearly communicate any technical issues or moderation needs to the live anchor and relevant team members.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain a positive and professional demeanor within the team environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent attention to detail and ability to identify and address potential problems proactively.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A keen eye for inappropriate content and a commitment to maintaining a positive online environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Effective communication and collaboration skills to work seamlessly within a team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to stay calm under pressure and make quick decisions in fast-paced situations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficient in (Thai, and English) to understand viewer comments and communicate effectively.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong technical skills with experience in live streaming software and platforms (OBS, TikTok Live, Shopee Live, Lazada Live a plus).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Graduating from relevant fields of study would be preferred.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Obtain and maintain a thorough understanding of the financial reporting and general ledger structure&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare&amp;nbsp;timely financial reports &amp;amp; to ensure compliance of Financial statement are recorded accurately and timely&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare standard supplemental reporting that provides analytical insight into the financial drivers of P&amp;amp;L / balance sheet performance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Liase with External Auditor &amp;amp; responsible for financial auditing process and reporting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist the Management with our annual budgeting process together with FP&amp;amp;A&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare adhoc reporting to support financial line item investigation and resolution also conduct adhoc analysis to support senior management decisions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and propose opportunities to increase overall company profitability&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Control NWC (AR-INV/AP) &amp;amp; Fixed Asset Management&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely and coordinate with other teams to ensure compliance with Finance Policies and Procedures&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Improve and develop the business process and procedures&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Control of Tax Compliance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Any other ad-hoc duties assigned.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Requirements:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s degree in Accounting.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Minimum 5–7 years of relevant accounting experience, preferably with prior experience in a Public Accounting Firm (KAP).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong knowledge and hands-on experience in financial reporting, monthly and annual closing, and account reconciliation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience managing and reviewing general ledger, balance sheet, and profit &amp;amp; loss statements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiar with Indonesian accounting standards (PSAK) and applicable tax regulations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven experience working with external auditors (e.g. Big Four), including audit coordination and preparation of audited financial statements drafts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in leading or mentoring accounting staff is a plus.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong analytical skills, attention to detail, and ability to work under tight deadlines.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Good communication and stakeholder management skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job purpose&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Corporate Finance &amp;amp; Investor Relations role in aCommerce is a combination of managing the company&#39;s funding and relationship with banks, regulators and investors, plus managing the M&amp;amp;A strategy going forward.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role will assist in driving the strategy, communication and interaction between aCommerce Public Company and our respective Investors, regulators and Stakeholders. The role will report to our Head of Corporate Finance and partner with our finance &amp;amp; FP&amp;amp;A team regionally and related department in crafting an IR strategy that builds long-term relationships with both the buy-side and sell-side community, while building a proactive strategy to grow and strengthen our investor base over time.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Duties and responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage the investor relations function and be the contact point for Company’s stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist in Company’s fund raising activities and liaise with financial advisors, regulators and investors&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Organize and conduct meetings with investors (conferences, roadshows, capital market days)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare monthly and quarterly shareholders update and ad-hoc analysis upon request&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Respond to investor queries and ensuring that all investor queries are dealt with in a timely manner&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare, in collaboration with the team, management talking points, presentations, press release, annual report, quarterly earnings, website and other relevant communication materials for investment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare financial models and relevant financial analyses for Company’s long term strategic planning&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Play the key role in potential capital market transaction and M&amp;amp;A deals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Other ad-hoc project assigned by Group CFO &amp;amp; Head of Corporate Finance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Capabilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3+ years of experience in corporate finance or related advisory roles&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Banking experience is a plus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor&#39;s degree in economics, finance, or related field&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledgeable in mergers and acquisitions, IPO, investor relations; including common valuation methodologies, financial modelling, etc.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent written communication and presentation skills are essential&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Able to explain complex topics in a clear, simple, and concise manner.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exceptional attention to detail combined with strong organizational skills, the ability to multi-task and strong follow up skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
